		WARP WARS

	You are the captian of the dreadnought Atlantic,
travelling in convoy with five sister ships.  Suddenly,
alarm bells ring as you notice one of your convoy
being torn apart by the awesome Planes of Dissimilation!
Quickly you scan nearby space and locate the interloper--
a Stilleto-class enemy 'Plaer' warship.  Obviously armed
with Planes of Dissimilation, the Plaer has pierced space
into the midst of your convoy.
	Your job (and you now have no choice but to accept
it) is to destroy the interloper before he dissimilates
your entire convoy.


