	You may assign a separate set of orders to each of
your six ships.  Each set of orders contains TWIRL commands,
structured status tests, and subroutine linkages.  The TWIRL
command allows you to specify any mix of speeds, thrusters,
and attitude control.  The structured tests (DOUNTIL, IF, 
ELSE), together with over ten status codes, allow dynamic
updates to the TWIRL commands.

	A test system is now available to run your attack/
defend strategies against a lone intelligent Plaer. Various
types of competition against other captians are being 
developed.  Suggestions welcome.  Interested?  See GregR.

